article_id:2147,category_name:News,title_name:Daily Free Summon Event Incoming!,image_path:,message:<div>A daily free summon event, which allows you to perform one summon on the applicable summon showcase for free once per day, will be live for the following duration!</div><div><br></div><div>■Event Duration</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1619589600"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1620885599"></span></div><div><br></div><div>■Applicable Summon Showcase</div><div>Whichever showcase is active during the event (excluding platinum showcases). The text &quot;One free summon!&quot; will appear over the Daily Deal button on the applicable showcase&#39;s summon screen.</div><div><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div>1. You can perform one summon for free on the applicable summon showcase once per day (each day is from 07:00 to 06:59 the following day).</div><div>2. The daily free summon resets each day at 07:00.</div><div>3. The Daily Deal, which allows you to summon once per day for 30 diamantium, will become available after performing your daily free summon.</div><div>4. For more information about summoning, tap Summon on the in-game footer menu, then select Showcase Info and check the Details tab.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1619503200,update_time1618982633